</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8B07431634FFDBB59EE7B96AF4C987" blockId="34.[160,1155,1146,1275]" pageId="34" pageNumber="350">
<taxonomicName id="4C347CC01634FFDBB59EE7B96A0EC9CA" baseAuthorityName="Nylander" baseAuthorityYear="1849" box="[160,343,1182,1206]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Pheidole" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="34" pageNumber="350" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pallidula">
<emphasis id="B940DB511634FFDBB59EE7B96A0EC9CA" box="[160,343,1182,1206]" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="350">Pheidole pallidula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a broad distribution in the Mediterranean region (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA57AB21634FFDBB6ADE7B96F7AC9CA" author="Bernard F" box="[915,1059,1182,1206]" pageId="34" pageNumber="350" refId="ref17587" refString="Bernard F. 1983. Encyclopedie entomologique - XLV. Les fourmis et leur milieu en France mediterraneenne. Paris: Editions Lechevalier; 149 pp." type="book" year="1983">Bernard 1983</bibRefCitation>
) and has been recorded from the Iberian Peninsula (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA57AB21634FFDBB74FE7E6684EC9A5" author="Espadaler X" box="[625,791,1217,1241]" pageId="34" pageNumber="350" pagination="109 - 126" refId="ref18565" refString="Espadaler X. 1986. VIII. Formicidos de los alrededores de La Laguna de Sarinena (Huesca). Descripcion del macho de Camponotus foreli Emery (Hym. Formicidae). Coleccion de Estudios Altoaragoneses. 6: 109 - 126." type="journal article" year="1986">Espadaler 1986</bibRefCitation>
). Our collections represent a new record for 
<collectingCountry id="F32347D31634FFDBB42EE7C46AF0C987" box="[272,425,1251,1275]" name="Socotra Island" pageId="34" pageNumber="350">Socotra Island</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
